Package com.udeyrishi.pipe.repository

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MutableRepository<T extends Identifiable>
    Extends interface Repository by adding mutability to it. Implementations must be thread-safe.
    Record<T extends Identifiable>
    Represents a unique item, and its metadata, as present in a interface Repository.
    Repository<T extends Identifiable>
    An abstract read-only key-value store of interface Identifiable items.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InMemoryRepository<T extends Identifiable>
    A simple, HashMap backed in-memory implementation of interface MutableRepository.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DuplicateUUIDException
    Thrown by MutableRepository.add if a second entry with an already used UUID is added.
